,A deep pan base is a type of pizza base. It is different from a thin and crispy base.,2,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#Capricciosa,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Capricciosa is a unique type of pizza known for its specific toppings. It includes peperonata, olives, capers, mozzarella, anchovies, ham, and tomatoes. This pizza is distinct because it combines these ingredients in a way that no other pizza does. Capricciosa stands apart from other varieties like la reine, frutti di mare, fiorentina, margherita, sloppy giuseppe, veneziana, american hot, unclosed pizza, mushroom, pollo ad astra, caprina, cajun, giardiniera, american, prince carlo, siciliana, parmense, rosa, soho, quattro formaggi, four seasons, and napoletana.",31,True

,Chicken topping is a type of meat topping. It is also a type of topping that has at least some mild spiciness. Unlike pepperoni sausage topping, hot spiced beef topping, and ham topping, chicken topping stands out as different.",5,True
,Meat topping is a type of pizza topping. It is different from cheese topping, fruit topping, herb spice topping, fish topping, nut topping, sauce topping, and vegetable topping.",8,True

,Anchovies topping is a type of fish topping. It's distinct from mixed seafood topping and also different from prawns topping.,3,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#Cajun,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Cajun is a unique type of pizza. It features a combination of toppings that include mozzarella, onion, peperonata, prawns, Tabasco pepper sauce, and tomato. This pizza must have at least some of each of these toppings: mozzarella, onion, tomato, peperonata, prawns, and Tabasco pepper sauce. Cajun pizza stands out from other varieties such as La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, Veneziana, American Hot, Sloppy Giuseppe, and many more including Mushroom, Caprina, Pollo ad Astra, Giardiniera, American, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",30,True

,Parmense is a unique type of named pizza. It exclusively features a combination of toppings including tomato, asparagus, mozzarella, parmesan, and ham. Additionally, Parmense must have at least some mozzarella, tomato, parmesan, asparagus, and ham toppings. Unlike other pizzas such as La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, American Hot, Veneziana, Sloppy Giuseppe, Unclosed Pizza, Mushroom, Pollo ad Astra, Caprina, Cajun, Giardiniera, American, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana, Parmense stands out with its distinct set of ingredients.",29,True

,Frutti di Mare is a type of pizza known for its unique toppings. It features a combination of garlic, mixed seafood, and tomato toppings. This pizza must include at least some tomato, mixed seafood, and garlic toppings. Unlike other pizzas, Frutti di Mare stands out and is distinct from La Reine, Fiorentina, Margherita, Sloppy Giuseppe, Veneziana, American Hot, Unclosed Pizza, Mushroom, Pollo ad Astra, Caprina, Cajun, Giardiniera, American, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",27,True
,Spiciness is a type of value partition. It is the same as the union of hot, medium, and mild.",2,True
,Fruit topping is a type of pizza topping. Unlike cheese, herb spice, meat, fish, sauce, nut, and vegetable toppings, fruit topping stands out as a unique option.",8,True

,A vegetarian pizza is equivalent to something that intersects with a pizza and has toppings that include a combination of fruit toppings, herb spice toppings, nut toppings, sauce toppings, vegetable toppings, and cheese toppings.",1,True

,Leek topping is a type of vegetable topping that has a mild spiciness. Unlike pepper topping, petit pois topping, spinach topping, caper topping, garlic topping, mushroom topping, tomato topping, rocket topping, onion topping, olive topping, asparagus topping, and artichoke topping, leek topping stands out with its unique flavor profile.",14,True

,Jalapeno pepper topping is a type of pepper topping that is known for its spiciness and heat. Unlike peperonata topping, green pepper topping, and sweet pepper topping, jalapeno pepper topping stands out with its unique fiery kick.",5,True

,Artichoke topping is a type of vegetable topping that has a mild level of spiciness. Unlike pepper topping, petit pois topping, leek topping, spinach topping, caper topping, garlic topping, mushroom topping, tomato topping, asparagus topping, onion topping, olive topping, and rocket topping, artichoke topping stands out with its unique flavor profile.",14,True

,Sundried tomato topping is a type of tomato topping. It is also a kind of topping that has at least some mild spiciness. Additionally, sundried tomato topping is different from sliced tomato topping.",3,True

,The Four Seasons is a type of named pizza that includes a variety of toppings. It must have at least some tomato, anchovies, mushrooms, pepperoni sausage, mozzarella, capers, and olives. Specifically, it only includes toppings that are a combination of anchovies, capers, mozzarella, mushrooms, olives, pepperoni sausage, and tomatoes. The Four Seasons pizza is distinct from other pizzas like La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, American Hot, Veneziana, Sloppy Giuseppe, and many others including Caprina, Pollo ad Astra, Cajun, Giardiniera, American, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, and Napoletana.",31,True

,Napoletana is a type of pizza that includes toppings like anchovies, capers, mozzarella, olives, and tomatoes. It's distinct from other pizzas such as La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, American Hot, Sloppy Giuseppe, Veneziana, Unclosed Pizza, Mushroom, Caprina, Pollo ad Astra, Cajun, Giardiniera, American, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, and Four Seasons.",29,True
,A sauce topping is a type of pizza topping. It's distinct from other toppings like fruit, cheese, herb and spice, meat, fish, nut, and vegetable toppings.",8,True

,Margherita is a type of pizza that includes at least some mozzarella and tomato toppings. It specifically has a combination of mozzarella and tomato toppings. Margherita is distinct from other pizzas such as La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Sloppy Giuseppe, American Hot, Veneziana, Unclosed Pizza, Mushroom, Pollo ad Astra, Caprina, Cajun, American, Giardiniera, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",26,True

,The Veneziana is a unique type of pizza that comes with a variety of toppings. It includes tomato, capers, pine kernels, mozzarella, onions, sultanas, and olives. All these toppings are combined to create a distinct flavor profile. The Veneziana is different from many other pizzas such as La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, Sloppy Giuseppe, American Hot, and many more. Each of these pizzas has its own unique set of ingredients and flavors, making the Veneziana stand out with its specific combination of toppings.",31,True
,Cajun spice topping is a type of herb spice topping. It also has a certain level of spiciness and heat. Unlike rosemary topping, Cajun spice topping has a distinct flavor profile.",3,True
,Pizza is a type of domain concept. It is also a type of something that at least has some pizza base. Pizza is different from ice cream, pizza base, and pizza topping.",5,True

,Prince Carlo is a unique type of named pizza. It comes with a variety of toppings, including rosemary, mozzarella, tomato, parmesan, and leek. The pizza is a combination of these specific toppings: leek, mozzarella, parmesan, rosemary, and tomato. Prince Carlo stands out from other pizzas like La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, American Hot, Veneziana, Sloppy Giuseppe, Mushroom, Caprina, Pollo ad Astra, Cajun, American, Giardiniera, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",29,True

,Pepperoni sausage topping is a type of meat topping that has a medium level of spiciness. Unlike chicken topping, hot spiced beef topping, and ham topping, pepperoni sausage topping stands out with its unique flavor.",5,True
,Peperonata topping is a type of pepper topping that has a medium level of spiciness. It's distinct from jalapeno pepper topping, sweet pepper topping, and green pepper topping.",5,True

,A spicy topping is the same as a pizza topping that intersects with something that has at least some hot spiciness.,1,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#ParmesanTopping,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
,Parmesan topping is a type of cheese topping that has a mild spiciness. It's distinct from goat cheese topping, gorgonzola topping, mozzarella topping, and four cheeses topping.",6,True

,Sloppy Giuseppe is a type of pizza that includes toppings like hot spiced beef, mozzarella, tomato, onion, and green pepper. It's unique in that it only features a combination of these specific toppings. Additionally, Sloppy Giuseppe stands out as it is different from a variety of other pizzas, including La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, Veneziana, American Hot, and many more such as Mushroom, Pollo ad Astra, Caprina, Cajun, American, Giardiniera, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",29,True

,Cheesy pizza is the same as a pizza that has some cheese topping.,1,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#SweetPepperTopping,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Sweet pepper topping is a type of pepper topping. It has some mild spiciness. Unlike jalapeno pepper topping, peperonata topping, and green pepper topping, sweet pepper topping has its own unique flavor.",5,True

,Pine kernels are a type of nut topping.,1,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#VegetarianPizzaEquivalent1,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,A vegetarian pizza is the same as a pizza that has only vegetarian toppings.,1,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#FishTopping,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Fish topping is a type of pizza topping. It is a kind of topping that at least has some mild spiciness. Unlike cheese, fruit, herb spice, meat, nut, vegetable, and sauce toppings, fish topping stands out with its unique flavor profile.",9,True

,Tomato topping is a type of vegetable topping. It has a mild spiciness. Unlike pepper topping, leek topping, petit pois topping, spinach topping, caper topping, garlic topping, mushroom topping, asparagus topping, rocket topping, olive topping, onion topping, and artichoke topping, tomato topping stands out with its unique characteristics.",14,True

,American Hot is a type of pizza known for its distinctive toppings. It features mozzarella and tomato toppings, along with hot green peppers, jalapeno peppers, peperoni sausage, and a combination of these ingredients. This pizza stands out from others like La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, Sloppy Giuseppe, Veneziana, and many more including Mushroom, Caprina, Pollo ad Astra, Cajun, Giardiniera, American, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",29,True

,The concept of value partition is different from that of a domain concept.,1,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#Caprina,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Caprina is a type of pizza that features several specific toppings. It includes some tomato topping, some mozzarella topping, some sundried tomato topping, and some cobertura de queijo de cabra. Essentially, Caprina is topped with a combination of cobertura de queijo de cabra, mozzarella, sundried tomatoes, and tomatoes.

Caprina stands out from other pizzas like La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, American Hot, Sloppy Giuseppe, Veneziana, and many others. It is distinct from pizzas such as Mushroom, Pollo ad Astra, Cajun, American, Giardiniera, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",28,True

,Pepper topping is a type of vegetable topping. It stands out from other toppings like petit pois, leek, spinach, caper, garlic, mushroom, tomato, olive, rocket, onion, asparagus, and artichoke.",13,True

,The Siciliana is a unique type of pizza known for its specific toppings. It includes ham, tomato, artichoke, garlic, anchovies, mozzarella, and olives. These toppings combine to create a distinctive flavor profile. Unlike other pizzas such as La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, American Hot, Veneziana, Sloppy Giuseppe, and many others, the Siciliana stands out with its particular combination of ingredients.",31,True

,Interesting pizza is the same as a pizza that has at least three toppings.,1,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#RealItalianPizza,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Real Italian pizza is a type of pizza that only has a thin and crispy base. It is the same as a pizza that must have Italy as its country of origin.,2,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#SpicyPizza,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Spicy pizza is the same as a pizza that has at least some spicy toppings.,1,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#SultanaTopping,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
,Sultana topping is a type of fruit topping. Additionally, it has a certain level of spiciness, specifically some medium spiciness.",2,True
,Herb spice topping is a type of pizza topping. Unlike cheese, fruit, meat, fish, vegetable, nut, or sauce toppings, herb spice topping stands out with its unique flavor profile.",8,True
,Gorgonzola topping is a type of cheese topping that has a mild spiciness. It is distinct from goat cheese topping, mozzarella topping, parmesan topping, and four cheeses topping.",6,True

,The American pizza is a unique type of pizza that includes toppings such as pepperoni sausage, mozzarella, and tomato. It combines these ingredients to create a distinct flavor. Unlike other pizzas, the American pizza stands apart from varieties like La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, Veneziana, Sloppy Giuseppe, American Hot, and even the unclosed pizza. It also differs from Mushroom, Caprina, Pollo ad Astra, Cajun, Giardiniera, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",27,True
,Ice cream is a type of domain concept. It is also a type of dessert that at least has some fruit topping. Ice cream is different from pizza, pizza base, and pizza topping.",5,True
,A vegetarian topping is the same as a pizza topping that is an intersection of vegetable, cheese, herb spice, fruit, nut, and sauce toppings.",1,True
,A cheesy vegetable topping is a type of cheese topping, and it's also a type of vegetable topping.",2,True

,Pollo ad Astra is a unique type of pizza. It features a variety of toppings, including garlic, tomato, mozzarella, Cajun spice, chicken, red onion, and sweet pepper. This pizza is distinct because it includes all these toppings together. Pollo ad Astra stands out from other pizzas such as La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, Veneziana, American Hot, Sloppy Giuseppe, and many others like Mushroom, Caprina, Cajun, American, Giardiniera, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",31,True
,A country is the same as a domain concept that intersects with America, England, France, Germany, and Italy.",1,True

,Mushroom topping is a type of vegetable topping and has a mild spiciness. Unlike pepper, leek, petit pois, spinach, caper, garlic, tomato, olive, asparagus, rocket, onion, and artichoke toppings, mushroom topping stands out with its unique flavor.",14,True

,An unclosed pizza is a unique type of pizza that always includes some mozzarella topping. It's distinct from many other well-known pizzas such as la reine, frutti di mare, fiorentina, margherita, american hot, sloppy giuseppe, veneziana, mushroom, pollo ad astra, caprina, cajun, giardiniera, american, prince carlo, capricciosa, siciliana, parmense, rosa, soho, quattro formaggi, four seasons, and napoletana.",24,True

,Onion topping is a type of vegetable topping that has a medium level of spiciness. Unlike pepper topping, petit pois topping, leek topping, spinach topping, caper topping, garlic topping, mushroom topping, tomato topping, asparagus topping, olive topping, rocket topping, and artichoke topping, onion topping stands out with its unique characteristics.",14,True
,Cobertura de queijo de cabra is a type of cheese topping that has a mild spiciness. It's distinct from other toppings like gorgonzola, mozzarella, parmesan, and four cheeses.",6,True

,Rosa is a unique type of pizza. It features toppings like gorgonzola, mozzarella, and tomato. Unlike many other pizzas, Rosa stands out with its distinct combination of flavors. It's different from popular varieties such as La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, Sloppy Giuseppe, American Hot, Veneziana, Mushroom, Pollo ad Astra, Caprina, Cajun, American, Giardiniera, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",27,True

,Mixed seafood topping is a type of fish topping. It is different from anchovies topping and also different from prawns topping.,3,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#NamedPizza,@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

,A named pizza is a type of pizza.,1,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#PrawnsTopping,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Prawns topping is a type of fish topping. It's different from mixed seafood topping and also distinct from anchovies topping.,3,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#CheeseTopping,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
,Cheese topping is a type of pizza topping. It's distinct from other toppings such as fruit, herb spice, meat, fish, vegetable, nut, and sauce toppings.",8,True

,Hot is a type of spiciness. It is different from medium and mild.,3,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#FourCheesesTopping,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,The four cheeses topping is a type of cheese topping. It is a variety that has at least some mild spiciness. Unlike other toppings, the four cheeses topping is distinct from cobertura de queijo de cabra, gorgonzola topping, mozzarella topping, and parmesan topping.",6,True
,A pizza topping is considered a type of domain concept. It's distinct from pizza itself, as well as from ice cream and the pizza base.",4,True

,La Reine is a specific type of pizza. It is uniquely topped with a combination of ham, mozzarella, mushrooms, olives, and tomatoes. Additionally, it must have at least some mozzarella, olive, mushroom, ham, and tomato toppings. La Reine stands apart from other pizzas such as Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, American Hot, Sloppy Giuseppe, Veneziana, Unclosed Pizza, Mushroom, Caprina, Pollo ad Astra, Cajun, American, Giardiniera, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",29,True

,Mild is a type of spiciness. It is different from hot and also distinct from medium.,3,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#MozzarellaTopping,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Mozzarella topping is a type of cheese topping that must originate from Italy and has a mild level of spiciness. It is distinct from goat cheese topping, gorgonzola topping, parmesan topping, and four cheeses topping.",7,True

,Hot spiced beef topping is a type of meat topping. It is characterized by its spiciness and heat. Unlike pepperoni sausage topping, chicken topping, and ham topping, hot spiced beef topping stands out with its unique flavor profile.",5,True
,Rosemary topping is a type of herb spice topping. It has some mild spiciness. Unlike rosemary topping, Cajun spice topping is different.",3,True
,Parma ham topping is a type of ham topping. Additionally, it is a type of topping that has at least some mild spiciness.",2,True

,Caper topping is a type of vegetable topping that has a mild spiciness. Unlike pepper topping, petit pois topping, leek topping, spinach topping, garlic topping, mushroom topping, tomato topping, asparagus topping, olive topping, onion topping, rocket topping, and artichoke topping, caper topping stands out with its unique characteristics.",14,True

,Medium is a type of spiciness. It is distinct from hot and also different from mild.,3,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#HotGreenPepperTopping,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
,A hot green pepper topping is a kind of green pepper topping. Additionally, it is a type of topping that has some level of spiciness.",2,True

,A thin and crispy base is a type of pizza base. It's different from a deep pan base.,2,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#NonVegetarianPizza,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Non-vegetarian pizza is different from vegetarian pizza. Non-vegetarian pizza is the same as the combination of the complement of vegetarian pizza and regular pizza.,2,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#SlicedTomatoTopping,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
,Sliced tomato topping is a type of tomato topping. It is also a type of topping that has at least some mild spiciness. Unlike sundried tomato topping, sliced tomato topping is different.",3,True
,Nut topping is a type of pizza topping that has some mild spiciness. Unlike fruit, cheese, herb spice, meat, fish, vegetable, and sauce toppings, nut topping stands out as a unique option.",9,True
,Green pepper topping is a type of pepper topping. It's distinct from jalapeno pepper topping, peperonata topping, and sweet pepper topping.",4,True

,A domain concept is different from a value partition.,1,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#Fiorentina,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Fiorentina is a type of pizza that comes with various toppings. It includes olives, mozzarella, garlic, spinach, tomatoes, and Parmesan cheese. Unlike other pizzas, Fiorentina exclusively features a combination of Parmesan, tomato, mozzarella, spinach, garlic, and olive toppings. It stands out from other pizzas like La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Margherita, American Hot, Veneziana, Sloppy Giuseppe, and many others. Each of these pizzas has its unique characteristics, making Fiorentina distinct in its own right.",30,True

,Quattro Formaggi is a type of pizza known for its four cheese toppings. It not only includes these cheeses but also has tomato toppings. Unlike many other pizzas, Quattro Formaggi is distinct from La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, Veneziana, Sloppy Giuseppe, American Hot, and even unclosed pizzas. It stands apart from Mushroom, Pollo ad Astra, Caprina, Cajun, Giardiniera, American, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",26,True

,Asparagus topping is a type of vegetable topping that has a mild spiciness. It is distinct from pepper topping, leek topping, petit pois topping, spinach topping, caper topping, garlic topping, mushroom topping, tomato topping, olive topping, onion topping, rocket topping, and artichoke topping.",14,True
,A pizza base is a type of domain concept. It's distinct from pizza, ice cream, and pizza topping.",4,True

,Giardiniera is a unique type of pizza that stands out with its distinctive toppings. It includes a variety of toppings such as mushrooms, leeks, peperonata, sliced tomatoes, mozzarella, olives, tomatoes, and petit pois. This pizza combines all these ingredients, creating a delightful union of flavors. Unlike other pizzas, giardiniera is different from la reine, frutti di mare, fiorentina, margherita, american hot, sloppy giuseppe, veneziana, unclosed pizza, mushroom, pollo ad astra, caprina, cajun, american, prince carlo, capricciosa, siciliana, parmense, rosa, soho, quattro formaggi, four seasons, and napoletana.",32,True

,Vegetarian pizza is different from non-vegetarian pizza. Vegetarian pizza is the same as a pizza that does not have any meat or fish toppings.,2,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#TobascoPepperSauce,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Tobasco pepper sauce is a type of sauce topping. It is known for its spiciness and heat.,2,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#HamTopping,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
,Ham topping is a type of meat topping. It is different from pepperoni sausage topping, chicken topping, and hot spiced beef topping.",4,True
,A vegetable topping is a type of pizza topping. It's distinct from other toppings like cheese, fruit, herb spice, meat, fish, nut, and sauce toppings.",8,True

,Soho is a type of pizza that includes toppings like tomato, mozzarella, rocket, parmesan, garlic, and olives. It exclusively features a combination of these toppings. Additionally, Soho is distinct from other pizzas such as La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, American Hot, Veneziana, Sloppy Giuseppe, Mushroom, Pollo ad Astra, Caprina, Cajun, Giardiniera, American, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",30,True

,Red onion topping is a type of onion topping.,1,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#PetitPoisTopping,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Petit pois topping is a type of vegetable topping that has a mild spiciness. Unlike pepper, leek, spinach, caper, garlic, mushroom, tomato, olive, rocket, onion, asparagus, and artichoke toppings, petit pois topping stands out with its unique characteristics.",14,True

,Spinach topping is a type of vegetable topping that has a mild level of spiciness. Unlike pepper, leek, petit pois, caper, garlic, mushroom, tomato, olive, onion, asparagus, rocket, and artichoke toppings, spinach topping stands out with its unique characteristics.",14,True

,Garlic topping is a type of vegetable topping that has a medium level of spiciness. Unlike pepper topping, leek topping, petit pois topping, spinach topping, caper topping, mushroom topping, tomato topping, asparagus topping, onion topping, rocket topping, olive topping, and artichoke topping, garlic topping stands out with its unique characteristics.",14,True

,Meaty pizza is the same as a pizza that has at least some meat topping.,1,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#OliveTopping,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Olive topping is a type of vegetable topping that has a mild spiciness. It stands out from other toppings such as pepper, petit pois, leek, spinach, caper, garlic, mushroom, tomato, rocket, onion, asparagus, and artichoke.",14,True

,A mushroom pizza is a unique type of pizza that includes at least some mushroom topping, some tomato topping, and some mozzarella topping. It is specifically characterized by having toppings that combine mozzarella, mushroom, and tomato. This pizza stands out from others like la reine, frutti di mare, fiorentina, margherita, veneziana, american hot, sloppy giuseppe, unclosed pizza, pollo ad astra, caprina, cajun, american, giardiniera, prince carlo, capricciosa, siciliana, parmense, rosa, soho, quattro formaggi, four seasons, and napoletana.",27,True

,Spicy pizza is equivalent to a pizza that has at least some toppings which include a pizza topping that has at least some hot spiciness.,1,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#RocketTopping,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Rocket topping is a type of vegetable topping that has a medium level of spiciness. Unlike other toppings, rocket topping is distinct from pepper, leek, petit pois, spinach, caper, garlic, mushroom, tomato, onion, olive, asparagus, and artichoke toppings.",14,True
